content: With less than two months left, I would like to continue supporting the campaign whenever I have time. I often have an hour of open time, but not two consecutive hours. Is it okay to join, or should I wait until I have two consecutive hours blocked off for the call? (FYI, I've done phone banking three times and now feel comfortable to jump straight into calling.)
Absolutely!  As much time as you have available is appreciated!
Do you need help getting to the phone bank zoom?  Here is the link: https://democrats.zoom.us/j/96712252906?pwd=k2LsmwEa29ouOsms2bg848tspKooho.1
If you are experienced, you can just ask for the dialer link once you are in the zoom.
Thank you, I'll sign up for a few upcoming shifts.
